CodeDef always_fail OrderCheck 1
CodeDef always_fail Description Always fails
CodeDef always_fail Routine <<EOR
sub {
	my ($ref, $name, $value, $msg) = @_;
	return (0, $name, $msg || errmsg('failed'));
}
EOR
